# Canonical author identity for navimed-umb.
# Per git-mailmap(5): "<canonical-name> <canonical-email>  <commit-name> <commit-email>"
# Right side = pattern to match in commit metadata.
# Left side  = display form used by git log, git shortlog, git blame, GitHub UI.
#
# This file rewrites display only. The git object database is untouched —
# SHA, tags, DOI references remain stable.

